Genre - Enum in lab2.cscd211enums
Simple Genre enumerated type for the composition assignment.
The enums are declared as FICTION(10, "fiction"), NONFICTION(20, "non-fiction"), ROMANCE(5, "romance"), SCIFI(30, "sci-fi"), EDUCATION(15, "education");
